The source of the buildmerger standalone executable in the bin directory can be found at https://github.com/nxadm/OpenCSW-BuildMerger. 

A script to generate the standalone executable from the OpenCSW::BuildMerger Perl distribution (CPAN styled and installable) is included as https://github.com/nxadm/OpenCSW-BuildMerger/blob/master/bin/create_fatpacked_bin.sh.

All the Perl dependencies are included in the standalone executable.
